{% doc %}
  @prompt
    Layout & Content Options (for Customizer):
    Up to 4 collection blocks (editable number)
    Each block has:
    Collection image (custom upload or auto from collection)
    
    Title (editable)
    
    Subtext/Description (editable)
    
    Collection link
    
    Product count (optional toggle)
    
    Custom arrow icon (optional toggle)
    
    Section background color (editable)
    
    Padding top/bottom (editable)
    
    Option to hide/show entire section
    
    Design & Style:
    
    Grid layout (1 row, 2–4 columns)
    
    Each card has:
    
    Image fills top area
    
    Text (title + subtext) below image
    
    Arrow → icon in bottom-right
    
    Rounded corners, spacing, and clean modern UI
    
    Hover Effects (must-have):
    
    On hover:
    
    Arrow fades in (bottom right)
    
    Underline appears under title
    
    Subtext stays visible
    
    Smooth transitions (ease-in-out)
    
    Functional Notes:
    
    Responsive: stacks nicely on mobile (2 per row or 1)
    
    Each block links to respective collection page
    
    Optional ability to auto-fetch image from collection’s featured image, Here I want to set first collection in full width so here can you option for this and add this functionality?, 🧩 Features to Include (in Customize Panel):
    Each collection block (up to 4 blocks):
    
    ✅ Collection picker (or custom link)
    ✅ Title (editable)
    ✅ Subtext (editable)
    ✅ Product count toggle (optional)
    ✅ Custom image upload OR auto-fetch from collection
    ✅ Layout style: Full-image with text overlay OR Image-top + text-bottom
    
    🎨 Design Details:
    Block 1 (leftmost):
    
    Full-height image (no card padding)
    
    Text overlay on top-left inside image (white text)
    
    Bottom: arrow icon → (on hover only)
    
    No visible title outside image
    
    Block 2, 3, 4:
    
    Image top, text (title + subtitle) bottom
    
    Clean white background
    
    Arrow → icon bottom-right (appears on hover)
    
    Title gets underline on hover
    
    🖱️ Hover Functionality:
    On hover:
    
    Arrow icon appears (fade in, bottom right)
    
    Title underlines
    
    Smooth transitions
    
    📱 Responsiveness:
    Mobile: stack 1 per row or 2x2
    
    All images should auto-resize proportionally
    
    🧰 Global Section Settings:
    Section background color (editable)
    Padding top/bottom (editable)
    Max number of cards (1–4)
    Option to hide/show product count
    Option to auto-pull collection image, Overview:
    Create a 4-block section to showcase collections in a modern grid. Each block design is different, as shown below. All blocks are clickable and customizable via theme editor.
    
    🔳 Layout & Functionality Details:
    Block 1 (Leftmost):
    Full-height background image
    
    Text overlays at bottom:
    
    Title (bold, white): Shop All
    
    Subtext: Check out all ou

{% enddoc %}
{% assign ai_gen_id = block.id | replace: '_', '' | downcase %}

{% style %}
  .ai-collection-showcase-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.background_color }};
    padding: {{ block.settings.section_padding }}px;
  }

  .ai-collection-showcase__container-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .ai-collection-showcase__grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat({{ block.settings.columns_desktop }}, 1fr);
    gap: {{ block.settings.grid_gap }}px;
    align-items: stretch;
  }

  .ai-collection-card-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: relative;
    display: block;
    text-decoration: none;
    color: inherit;
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.border_radius }}px;
    overflow: hidden;
    height: {{ block.settings.card_height }}px;
  }

  .ai-collection-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}--featured {
    position: relative;
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
    background-repeat: no-repeat;
  }

  .ai-collection-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}--featured::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(0,0,0,0.3) 0%, rgba(0,0,0,0.6) 100%);
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .ai-collection-card__featured-content-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    padding: {{ block.settings.featured_padding }}px;
    z-index: 2;
    color: white;
  }

  .ai-collection-card__featured-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.featured_title_size }}px;
    font-weight: {{ block.settings.featured_title_weight }};
    margin: 0 0 8px 0;
    line-height: 1.2;
    color: {{ block.settings.featured_text_color }};display: flex;
    align-items: center;gap: 8px;
  }

  .ai-collection-card__featured-subtitle-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.featured_subtitle_size }}px;
    margin: 0;
    opacity: 0.9;
    line-height: 1.4;
    color: {{ block.settings.featured_text_color }};
  }

  .ai-collection-card__featured-count-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: 12px;
    opacity: 0.8;
    margin-left: 4px;
  }

  .ai-collection-card__featured-arrow-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    color: {{ block.settings.featured_text_color }};
    transition: transform {{ block.settings.animation_speed }}ms ease-in-out;
    transform: rotate(0deg);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .ai-collection-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}--featured:hover .ai-collection-card__featured-arrow-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    transform: rotate(90deg);
  }

  .ai-collection-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}--standard {
    background-color: {{ block.settings.card_background }};
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease-in-out;
  }

  .ai-collection-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}--standard:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .ai-collection-card__image-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: relative;
    width: 100%;
    height: 60%;
    overflow: hidden;
    border-radius: {{ block.settings.border_radius }}px {{ block.settings.border_radius }}px 0 0;
  }

  .ai-collection-card__image-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;}

  .ai-collection-card__image-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    background-color: #f4f4f4;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .ai-collection-card__image-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }} svg {
    width: 60px;
    height: 60px;
    opacity: 0.5;
  }

  .ai-collection-card__content-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    padding: {{ block.settings.content_padding }}px;
    flex-grow: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    justify-content: flex-end;
    position: relative;
  }

  .ai-collection-card__content-top-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    margin-top: auto;
  }

  .ai-collection-card__title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.title_size }}px;
    font-weight: {{ block.settings.title_weight }};
    margin: 0 0 8px 0;
    color: {{ block.settings.title_color }};
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    line-height: 1.3;
  }

  .ai-collection-card__title-text-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    position: relative;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .ai-collection-card__title-text-{{ ai_gen_id }}::after {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    bottom: -2px;
    left: 0;
    width: 0;
    height: 2px;
    background-color: {{ block.settings.hover_underline_color }};
    transition: width 0.3s ease-in-out;
  }

  .ai-collection-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}--standard:hover .ai-collection-card__title-text-{{ ai_gen_id }}::after {
    width: 100%;
  }

  .ai-collection-card__subtitle-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: {{ block.settings.subtitle_size }}px;
    color: {{ block.settings.subtitle_color }};
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .ai-collection-card__count-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: {{ block.settings.subtitle_color }};
    opacity: 0.7;
    margin-left: 4px;
  }

  .ai-collection-card__arrow-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    color: {{ block.settings.hover_arrow_color }};
    transition: transform {{ block.settings.animation_speed }}ms ease-in-out;
    transform: rotate(0deg);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .ai-collection-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}--standard:hover .ai-collection-card__arrow-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
    transform: rotate(90deg);
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 989px) {
    .ai-collection-showcase-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding: {{ block.settings.section_padding | times: 0.8 }}px;
    }

    .ai-collection-showcase__grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      grid-template-columns: repeat({{ block.settings.columns_tablet }}, 1fr);
      gap: {{ block.settings.grid_gap | times: 0.8 }}px;
    }

    .ai-collection-card-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      height: {{ block.settings.card_height | times: 0.85 }}px;
    }

    .ai-collection-card__featured-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.featured_title_size | times: 0.9 }}px;
    }

    .ai-collection-card__title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.title_size | times: 0.9 }}px;
    }
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 749px) {
    .ai-collection-showcase-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding: {{ block.settings.section_padding | times: 0.6 }}px;
    }

    .ai-collection-showcase__grid-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      grid-template-columns: repeat({{ block.settings.columns_mobile }}, 1fr);
      gap: {{ block.settings.grid_gap | times: 0.6 }}px;
    }

    .ai-collection-card-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      height: {{ block.settings.card_height | times: 0.7 }}px;
    }

    .ai-collection-card__featured-content-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding: {{ block.settings.featured_padding | times: 0.7 }}px;
    }

    .ai-collection-card__content-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      padding: {{ block.settings.content_padding | times: 0.8 }}px;
    }

    .ai-collection-card__featured-title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.featured_title_size | times: 0.8 }}px;
    }

    .ai-collection-card__title-{{ ai_gen_id }} {
      font-size: {{ block.settings.title_size | times: 0.8 }}px;
    }
  }
{% endstyle %}

<div class="ai-collection-showcase-{{ ai_gen_id }}" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
  <div class="ai-collection-showcase__container-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
    <div class="ai-collection-showcase__grid-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
      {% for i in (1..4) %}
        {% liquid
          assign collection_key = 'collection_' | append: i
          assign title_key = 'title_' | append: i
          assign subtitle_key = 'subtitle_' | append: i
          assign custom_image_key = 'custom_image_' | append: i
          assign use_custom_image_key = 'use_custom_image_' | append: i

          assign collection = block.settings[collection_key]
          assign title = block.settings[title_key]
          assign subtitle = block.settings[subtitle_key]
          assign custom_image = block.settings[custom_image_key]
          assign use_custom_image = block.settings[use_custom_image_key]

          if collection != blank
            assign card_url = collection.url
            assign card_title = collection.title
            assign product_count = collection.products_count
          else
            assign card_url = '#'
            assign card_title = 'Collection'
            assign product_count = 0
          endif

          if title != blank
            assign card_title = title
          endif

          if use_custom_image and custom_image != blank
            assign card_image = custom_image
          elsif collection != blank and collection.featured_image
            assign card_image = collection.featured_image
          else
            assign card_image = null
          endif
        %}

        {% if i == 1 %}<a 
            href="{{ card_url }}" 
            class="ai-collection-card-{{ ai_gen_id }} ai-collection-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}--featured"
            {% if card_image %}
              style="background-image: url('{{ card_image | image_url: width: 800 }}');"
            {% endif %}
          >
            {% unless card_image %}
              <div class="ai-collection-card__image-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                {{ 'collection-1' | placeholder_svg_tag }}
              </div>
            {% endunless %}
            <div class="ai-collection-card__featured-content-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              <h3 class="ai-collection-card__featured-title-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                <span>{{ card_title }}</span>
                {% if block.settings.show_product_count and collection != blank %}
                  <span class="ai-collection-card__featured-count-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ product_count }}</span>
                {% endif %}
                <svg class="ai-collection-card__featured-arrow-{{ ai_gen_id }}" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                  <path d="m9 18 6-6-6-6"></path>
                </svg>
              </h3>
              {% if subtitle != blank %}
                <p class="ai-collection-card__featured-subtitle-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ subtitle }}</p>
              {% endif %}
            </div>
          </a>
        {% else %}
          <a 
            href="{{ card_url }}" 
            class="ai-collection-card-{{ ai_gen_id }} ai-collection-card-{{ ai_gen_id }}--standard"
          >
            <div class="ai-collection-card__image-wrapper-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              {% if card_image %}
                <img
                  src="{{ card_image | image_url: width: 600 }}"
                  alt="{{ card_image.alt | escape }}"
                  class="ai-collection-card__image-{{ ai_gen_id }}"
                  loading="lazy"
                width="600"
                  height="400"
                >
              {% else %}
                <div class="ai-collection-card__image-placeholder-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                  {{ 'collection-1' | placeholder_svg_tag }}
                </div>
              {% endif %}
            </div>

            <div class="ai-collection-card__content-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
              <div class="ai-collection-card__content-top-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                <h3 class="ai-collection-card__title-{{ ai_gen_id }}">
                  <span class="ai-collection-card__title-text-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ card_title }}</span>
                  {% if block.settings.show_product_count and collection != blank %}
                    <span class="ai-collection-card__count-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ product_count }}</span>
                  {% endif %}
                  <svg class="ai-collection-card__arrow-{{ ai_gen_id }}" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                    <path d="m9 18 6-6-6-6"></path>
                  </svg>
                </h3>
                
                {% if subtitle != blank %}
                  <p class="ai-collection-card__subtitle-{{ ai_gen_id }}">{{ subtitle }}</p>
                {% endif %}
              </div>
            </div>
          </a>
        {% endif %}
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

